---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | IK101">
  <SiteNav current="/about" />

  <main class="abt">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="abt-hero">
      <p class="abt-eyebrow">Spirit of IK101</p>
      <h1 class="abt-title">Not just a movement; IK101 is a call to action.</h1>
      <p class="abt-lede">At the heart of IK101 resonates the enduring legacy of Imran Khan - a life dedicated to the pursuit of a welfare state where every individual's rights are not merely acknowledged but fiercely protected. IK101 is a call to amplify your voice, connect with citizens globally, and contribute to building a truly independent, democratic, and progressive Pakistan.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- MOVEMENT INTRO -->
    <section class="abt-section abt-section--center">
      <p class="abt-body">You don't have to be in one place to be part of IK101. Jump into the action from grassroots engagement to the dynamic stage of IK101 Engage, a platform where your ideas for progress take life. Enrich our digital gallery, share your narratives and inspirations, and let's showcase the power of collective voices.</p>
      <a class="abt-cta" href="/ambassador">Join the movement!</a>
    </section>

    <!-- GRASSROOTS ROW: image left -->
    <section class="abt-features">

      <div class="abt-row">
        <div class="abt-row__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-row__img" src="/about/mail-ik101-postcard-mjE2o70jyaIV6QJg.png" alt="IK101 grassroots postcard campaign" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-row__body">
          <p class="abt-row__label">Grassroots Activation</p>
          <h2 class="abt-row__heading">Join us on a journey of grassroots change!</h2>
          <p class="abt-row__text">Become an #IK101 ambassador, undertake door-to-door campaign and spread the message of positive leadership and change. Every step, every conversation matters. Print, write, share.</p>
          <a class="abt-row__cta" href="/ambassador">Become an Ambassador &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ENGAGE ROW: image right -->
      <div class="abt-row abt-row--flip">
        <div class="abt-row__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-row__img" src="/about/ik101-engage-m7Vpe1BgQMS7r7G1.png" alt="IK101 Engage platform" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-row__body">
          <p class="abt-row__label">Engage <span class="abt-coming-soon">Coming Soon</span></p>
          <h2 class="abt-row__heading">IK101 Engage</h2>
          <p class="abt-row__text">IK101 Engage serves as a conduit linking global citizens to local visionaries committed to progress. Within this dynamic forum, dedicated Pakistanis find a stage to voice real community issues, discuss innovative solutions, and collaborate with a global audience to transform ideas into reality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- TRUTH TO POWER ROW: image left -->
      <div class="abt-row">
        <div class="abt-row__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-row__img" src="/about/logo---truth2power-AVLJeDGEKrTKplwR.png" alt="Truth 2 Power Hub logo" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-row__body">
          <p class="abt-row__label">Truth To Power Hub</p>
          <h2 class="abt-row__heading">Building a community of trust through truth-telling.</h2>
          <p class="abt-row__text">At IK101, we're building a community of trust through truth-telling. For every fake narrative, we promise 101 voices of truth. Join us in peaceful resistance as we build a digital archive of real stories, resilience and hope. Let's write our own history. If we don't, it will be written for us.</p>
          <a class="abt-row__cta" href="https://www.youtube.com/@truth2powerhub" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Truth To Power Hub &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- HAQIQI AZADI DIVIDER -->
    <section class="abt-azadi">
      <p class="abt-azadi__phrase">In my truly independent Pakistan...</p>
      <p class="abt-azadi__body">This phrase represents the beginning of a powerful dialogue, where every Pakistani can contribute their vision of what true independence means to them. Whether it's about justice, equality, education, or governance, we want to know: How do you picture Haqiqi Azadi?</p>
    </section>

    <!-- CAMPAIGNS GRID -->
    <section class="abt-campaigns">

      <div class="abt-campaign">
        <div class="abt-campaign__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-campaign__img" src="/about/myazadpak_website-mnl98wnqGQiGQbGe.png" alt="Azad Pakistan campaign" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-campaign__body">
          <h3 class="abt-campaign__heading">Azad Pakistan</h3>
          <a class="abt-campaign__link" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1y1wcxBcLuSPnApMP8oB-Bch9xHGqdhRs?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Resources &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="abt-campaign">
        <div class="abt-campaign__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-campaign__img" src="/about/sos---capt-gulsher-m7VKvOV2GniLR5oq.png" alt="SOS Captain Gulsher social media campaign" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-campaign__body">
          <h3 class="abt-campaign__heading">SOS CAPT. GULSHER</h3>
          <p class="abt-campaign__text">As Pakistan faced the aftermath of a regime change, Captain Gulsher, character of a young army officer known from the 90s Pakistani drama serial Sunehray Din, became the voice of the masses and a conduit between them and the ruling quarters. This powerful social media response relayed public reactions to the evolving situation post April 9th, 2022 regime change operation in Pakistan; and served as a rallying cry for true freedom.</p>
          <a class="abt-campaign__link" href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo91venkyugDJV90LZw4VLiQyN3QhAxNL&si=KhSMgN_gnF_rBqkr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SOS CAPT. GULSHER &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="abt-campaign">
        <div class="abt-campaign__img-wrap">
          <img class="abt-campaign__img" src="/about/symbols-of-democracy-mePnE7ORO4Feb540.png" alt="Symbols of Democracy campaign" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="abt-campaign__body">
          <h3 class="abt-campaign__heading">Symbols of Democracy</h3>
          <p class="abt-campaign__text">When the fascist regime in Pakistan tried to sabotage the 2024 general elections by taking away largest political party's election symbol (cricket bat), the IK101 Ambassadors sprang into action. They turned to social media and AI to creatively highlight each candidate's new symbol — from fruits and vegetables to everyday items — ensuring voters could still identify and support their preferred candidates.</p>
          <a class="abt-campaign__link" href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo91venkyugCHT44o-5zCIWY1Ba62JBOo&feature=shared" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Symbols of Democracy &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- CLOSING CTA -->
    <section class="abt-close">
      <h2 class="abt-close__heading">Let the world hear our collective voice, as we shape the narrative for a truly democratic Pakistan.</h2>
      <div class="abt-close__ctas">
        <a class="abt-close__btn abt-close__btn--primary" href="/ambassador">Join as Ambassador</a>
        <a class="abt-close__btn abt-close__btn--outline" href="/postcards">Explore Postcards</a>
      </div>
      <p class="abt-statement">My Voice, My Pakistan, My Movement.</p>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="abt-foot">
    <nav class="abt-foot-links">
      <a href="/#resources">Resources</a><a href="/connect">Connect</a><a href="/useful-links">Useful Links</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="abt-foot-copy">IK101 © 2023</p>
  </footer>

  <style is:global>
    /* ── About page — all classes prefixed .abt- ── */

    .abt {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) 1.25rem 2rem;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .abt-hero {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 66ch;
      margin: 0 auto clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    }
    .abt-eyebrow {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: .8rem;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }
    .abt-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.6vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -.025em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 auto 1.1rem;
      max-width: 24ch;
    }
    .abt-lede {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 62ch;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* CENTERED SECTION */
    .abt-section--center {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 62ch;
      margin: 0 auto clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    }
    .abt-body {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }
    .abt-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: .85rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: transform .2s var(--ease-out), filter .2s;
    }
    .abt-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      filter: brightness(1.06);
    }

    /* FEATURE ROWS */
    .abt-features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    }
    .abt-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .abt-row--flip {
      direction: rtl;
    }
    .abt-row--flip > * {
      direction: ltr;
    }
    .abt-row__img-wrap {
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 56px rgba(20, 40, 28, .13);
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      background: #f1f5f2;
    }
    .abt-row__img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .abt-row__body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .85rem;
    }
    .abt-row__label {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: .78rem;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .6rem;
    }
    .abt-coming-soon {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: .18rem .55rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
    }
    .abt-row__heading {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .abt-row__text {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .abt-row__cta {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: .7rem 1.5rem;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 100px;
      align-self: flex-start;
      transition: background .2s var(--ease-out), color .2s, transform .2s var(--ease-out);
    }
    .abt-row__cta:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--ink);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* HAQIQI AZADI DIVIDER */
    .abt-azadi {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--faint);
      padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem) 0;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 72ch;
      margin: 0 auto clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    }
    .abt-azadi__phrase {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    }
    .abt-azadi__body {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 60ch;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* CAMPAIGNS GRID */
    .abt-campaigns {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    }
    .abt-campaign {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      border: 1px solid var(--faint);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow .25s var(--ease-out), transform .25s var(--ease-out);
    }
    .abt-campaign:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(20, 40, 28, .12);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    .abt-campaign__img-wrap {
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f1f5f2;
    }
    .abt-campaign__img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      transition: transform .35s var(--ease-out);
    }
    .abt-campaign:hover .abt-campaign__img {
      transform: scale(1.04);
    }
    .abt-campaign__body {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .75rem;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .abt-campaign__heading {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .abt-campaign__text {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
      line-height: 1.62;
      margin: 0;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .abt-campaign__link {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .88rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: auto;
      transition: opacity .15s;
    }
    .abt-campaign__link:hover {
      opacity: .75;
    }

    /* CLOSING */
    .abt-close {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 60ch;
      margin: 0 auto clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    }
    .abt-close__heading {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
    }
    .abt-close__ctas {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .9rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    }
    .abt-close__btn {
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: .85rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: transform .2s var(--ease-out), filter .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .abt-close__btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .abt-close__btn--primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .abt-close__btn--primary:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.06);
    }
    .abt-close__btn--outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    }
    .abt-close__btn--outline:hover {
      background: var(--faint);
    }
    .abt-statement {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .abt-foot {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
      margin-top: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .abt-foot-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .abt-foot-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }
    .abt-foot-links a:hover {
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .abt-foot-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .8rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .abt-campaigns {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .abt-row,
      .abt-row--flip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        direction: ltr;
      }
      .abt-row--flip > * {
        direction: ltr;
      }
      .abt-row__img-wrap {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      }
      .abt-row__cta {
        align-self: stretch;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .abt-campaigns {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .abt-campaign,
      .abt-campaign__img { transition: none; }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
